!public/assets/RU/ISE507 Data Analytics In Engineering Systems/
public/assets/RU/ISE507 Data Analytics In Engineering Systems/*
!public/assets/RU/ISE507 Data Analytics In Engineering Systems/PROJECT/
public/assets/RU/ISE507 Data Analytics In Engineering Systems/PROJECT/*
!public/assets/RU/ISE507 Data Analytics In Engineering Systems/PROJECT/507ProjectPresentation.pdf
!public/assets/RU/ISE507 Data Analytics In Engineering Systems/PROJECT/507ProjectReport.pdf

# ise530-showcase → 4 PDFs only
